<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[تأَوَّل]</span> الآية والحديث.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[هـ‍]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[تأَوَّه]</span>: إِذا قال أَوْهِ،<span class="c5"> قال:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ولَرُبَّما ابْتَسَمَ الحَلِيمُ مِنَ الأَذَى ... وفُؤادُهُ مِنْ حَرِّهِ يَتَأوَّهُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
